1 Revisiting Lab 2

library(tidyverse)
library(here)
library(forcats)
surveys <- read_csv(here::here("supporting_artifacts" , "Datasets", "surveys.csv"))

1. Reorder

surveys <- surveys %>% 
  mutate(species = fct_reorder(
    species, weight, .desc=TRUE)
    )
ggplot(data = surveys, 
       mapping = aes(
         x = weight, y = species)
       ) +
  geom_jitter(color = "pink") +
  geom_boxplot() +
  labs(x = 'weight (grams)', y = 'species of rodents')

2. Y Axis Label at Top

ggplot(data = surveys, 
       mapping = aes(
         x = weight, y = species)
       ) +
  geom_jitter(color = "pink") +
  geom_boxplot() +
  labs(x = 'weight (grams)', y = '', 
  title = 'Distrubution of Weight by Rodent Species')

2 Time-Series Plot

1. Visualization

survey_summary <- surveys %>% 
  group_by(year, genus) %>% 
  summarize(across(
    weight, .fns = sum)
    )
ggplot(data = survey_summary, 
       mapping = aes(
         x = year, y = weight, color = genus)
       ) +
  geom_line()

2. Mean weight

survey_mean <- surveys %>% 
  group_by(year, genus) %>% 
  summarize(across(
      weight, .fns = mean)
    )
ggplot(data = survey_mean, 
       mapping = aes(
         x = year, y = weight, color = genus)
       ) +
  geom_line()

3. Reorder

ggplot(data = survey_mean, 
       mapping = aes(
         x = year, y = weight, color = fct_reorder2(
    genus, year, weight))
       ) +
  geom_line()

4. Title

ggplot(data = survey_mean, 
       mapping = aes(
         x = year, y = weight, color = fct_reorder2(
    genus, year, weight))
       ) +
  geom_line() +
  labs(x = 'Year', y = '', 
  title = 'Change in Average Weight by Rodent Genus',
  color = "Rodent Genus")

3 Captures over the Week

1. Visualization

survey_week <- surveys %>% 
  drop_na
ggplot(data = survey_week,
       mapping = aes(
         x = day_of_week)
       ) +
  geom_bar() +
  labs(x = 'Day of Week', y = '', 
  title = 'Number of Rodents Captured Each Day of the Week')

2. Reorder

ggplot(data = survey_week, 
       mapping = aes(
         x = day_of_week)
       ) +
  geom_bar() +
  labs(x = 'Day of Week', y = '', 
  title = 'Number of Rodents Captured Each Day of the Week')
